  <scopecontent id="aspace_3e44d32fa0e4a561dbd9f3979e3da342">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Correspondence, administrative papers, annual reports, records and logbooks, memoranda, statistical data, and a scrapbook of newspaper clippings pertaining to the operation of a tuberculosis sanatorium in Ithaca, New York.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <userestrict id="aspace_a88844b952972bd741b7938889df1668">
    <head>Restrictions on Use:</head>
<p>Information obtained from these records may not be published or otherwise released in such form that any individual patient mentioned in the records can be identified.</p>  </userestrict>
